WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.210
To expand internationally, firms use entry strategies like exporting, licensing, and contract manufacturing.

为了进行国际扩张，

企业会采用出口、
许可和合同制造等进入策略。

00:00:04.210 --> 00:00:09.250


00:00:09.250 --> 00:00:12.680
The choice of strategy is based on their goals, market conditions, and capabilities, each offering unique benefits and risks.

策略的选择取决于他们的目标、

市场条件和能力，

每种策略都具有独特的优势和风险。

00:00:12.680 --> 00:00:16.850


00:00:16.850 --> 00:00:18.790


00:00:18.790 --> 00:00:21.350
An American clothing brand, EcoStyle, may enter foreign markets by exporting and selling its clothing line to buyers using domestic intermediaries.

美国服装品牌环保风尚（EcoStyle）

能够通过出口

并利用国内中间商销售其服装系列给买家
来进入国外市场。

00:00:21.350 --> 00:00:24.390


00:00:24.390 --> 00:00:29.310


00:00:29.310 --> 00:00:32.110
This low-risk indirect exporting strategy allows the company to test the market with limited control over marketing activities.

这种低风险的间接出口策略

使得企业能够在对营销活动

控制有限的情况下测试市场。

00:00:32.110 --> 00:00:35.580


00:00:35.580 --> 00:00:38.450


00:00:38.450 --> 00:00:41.820
Eventually, it could export directly to foreign markets, yielding higher profits and control over business operations.

最终，

它能够直接出口到国外市场，

从而获得更高的利润和对业务运营的控制。

00:00:41.820 --> 00:00:44.020


00:00:44.020 --> 00:00:46.050


00:00:46.050 --> 00:00:49.940
But with higher investment and risk.

但是投资和风险会更高。

00:00:49.940 --> 00:00:53.090
Alternatively, Ecostyle could license its brand to reputable retailers or manufacturers abroad, allowing them to sell the products on its behalf.

或者，

环保风尚能够将其品牌授权给
国外知名的零售商或制造商，

从而允许他们代表自己销售产品。

00:00:53.090 --> 00:00:55.800


00:00:55.800 --> 00:01:00.310


00:01:00.310 --> 00:01:02.750
It can leverage the partners' market knowledge and distribution networks, minimizing financial risks.

它能够利用合作伙伴的市场知识

和分销网络来最大限度地降低财务风险。

00:01:02.750 --> 00:01:07.410


00:01:07.410 --> 00:01:11.560
Lastly, EcoStyle might opt for contract manufacturing by outsourcing production to manufacturers in cost-efficient regions.

最后，

环保风尚可能会选择合同制造，

从而将生产外包给
具有成本效益的地区的制造商。

00:01:11.560 --> 00:01:14.210


00:01:14.210 --> 00:01:16.990


00:01:16.990 --> 00:01:19.780
This strategy enables it to scale production while reducing manufacturing costs and distribution complexities.

这一策略使其能够扩大生产规模，

同时降低制造成本

和分销的复杂性。

00:01:19.780 --> 00:01:23.020


00:01:23.020 --> 00:01:24.430


00:01:24.430 --> 00:01:30.270
But, it increases risk due to less control over production.

但是，由于对生产的控制较少，
因此风险也会随之增加。
